messages.message: @Xindi Xu what class of errors would you be hoping to fix with this? Ones coming from the same test happening in multiple runs, for tests of apps and build projects?
there's only one cypress test run per pull request, but multiple pull requests

> Ones coming from the same test happening in multiple runs, for tests of apps and build projects?
Yep. I know that when I wrote cypress tests, I was assuming that the tests from the same spec file wouldn't run at the same time, but this assumption no longer holds when we have so many PRs running tests around the same time.

Weâ€™re talking in this thread about how to fix it for build projects: https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C05EQQJGN7L/p1715299455722119 (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C05EQQJGN7L/p1715299455722119)
